----------------------------
apache/mod-php for web retro
----------------------------

1. deps
 - php5-5.3.3
 - apache2.2.14-5

 make setup
 
2. rerun
 - set RETRO_RERUN=/tmp/logfile
 - run apache (./run.sh)

 make rerun

3. run
 - run apache (./run.sh)

 make run

* modify `RETRO_WEBDIR' (in run.sh) pointing to the directory of web documents
 